---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.tsx";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Sigel - Websites que Geram Clientes | Copywriting | Automação"
  description="Soluções completas em desenvolvimento web, copywriting e automação para PMEs. 100+ empresas atendidas. Diagnóstico gratuito."
  canonical="/"
>
  <Header client:load />

  {/* ===== HERO SECTION ===== */}
  <section
    class="relative px-5 md:px-12 pt-8 md:pt-24 pb-12 md:pb-24 w-full flex flex-col items-center bg-black"
  >
    {/* Stardust Pattern Background */}
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')] opacity-30"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10">
      {/* Decorative Blur Circles */}
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10 translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 md:w-80 h-48 md:h-80 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[80px] -z-10 -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/4"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 z-10 w-full">
        {/* LEFT: Text Content */}
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 w-full md:w-1/2">
          {/* Badge */}
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full w-fit"
          >
            <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
              <span
                class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-accent opacity-75"
              ></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-accent"
              ></span>
            </span>
            <span
              class="text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wide"
            >
              Soluções em Informática
            </span>
          </div>

          {/* Headline */}
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black leading-[1.2] tracking-tight text-white"
          >
            <span class="block mb-1 md:mb-2">Websites que geram clientes.</span>
            <span class="block mb-1 md:mb-2">Copy que vende.</span>
            <span
              class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent"
            >
              Automação que escala.
            </span>
          </h1>

          {/* Description */}
          <p
            class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-xl md:max-w-xl leading-relaxed"
          >
            Para pequenos e médios negócios. Entregamos sites rápidos, com texto
            estratégico e base prontos para vender com suporte contínuo.
          </p>

          {/* CTA Buttons */}
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mt-4 md:mt-6">
            <a
              href="https://wa.me/555191305583?text=Ol%C3%A1%21%20Estava%20no%20site%20da%20Sigel%20e%20gostaria%20de%20solicitar%20um%20diagn%C3%B3stico%20gratuito%20para%20o%20meu%20neg%C3%B3cio."
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="ring-4 ring-primary/40 animate-pulse w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-bold text-base md:text-lg h-14 md:h-16 px-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-[0.98]"
            >
              <span>Solicitar Diagnóstico</span>
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="22"
                height="22"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                <path
                  d="M13.601 2.326A7.85 7.85 0 0 0 7.994 0C3.627 0 .068 3.558.064 7.926c0 1.399.366 2.76 1.057 3.965L0 16l4.204-1.102a7.9 7.9 0 0 0 3.79.965h.004c4.368 0 7.926-3.558 7.93-7.93A7.9 7.9 0 0 0 13.6 2.326zM7.994 14.521a6.6 6.6 0 0 1-3.356-.92l-.24-.144-2.494.654.666-2.433-.156-.251a6.56 6.56 0 0 1-1.007-3.505c0-3.626 2.957-6.584 6.591-6.584a6.56 6.56 0 0 1 4.66 1.931 6.56 6.56 0 0 1 1.928 4.66c-.004 3.639-2.961 6.592-6.592 6.592m3.615-4.934c-.197-.099-1.17-.578-1.353-.646-.182-.065-.315-.099-.445.099-.133.197-.513.646-.627.775-.114.133-.232.148-.43.05-.197-.1-.836-.308-1.592-.985-.59-.525-.985-1.175-1.103-1.372-.114-.198-.011-.304.088-.403.087-.088.197-.232.296-.346.1-.114.133-.198.198-.33.065-.134.034-.248-.015-.347-.05-.099-.445-1.076-.612-1.47-.16-.389-.323-.335-.445-.34-.114-.007-.247-.007-.38-.007a.73.73 0 0 0-.529.247c-.182.198-.691.677-.691 1.654s.71 1.916.81 2.049c.098.133 1.394 2.132 3.383 2.992.47.205.84.326 1.129.418.475.152.904.129 1.246.08.38-.058 1.171-.48 1.338-.943.164-.464.164-.86.114-.943-.049-.084-.182-.133-.38-.232"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </a>

            <a
              href="/servicos"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-transparent border border-gray-700 hover:bg-white/5 text-white font-bold text-base md:text-lg h-14 md:h-16 px-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-[0.98]"
            >
              <span>Nossos Serviços</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          {/* Trust Message */}
          <p
            class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-medium"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] text-green-500"
              >verified</span
            >
            Não é uma ligação de vendas. É um raio-x gratuito do seu negócio.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* RIGHT: Laptop Image with Floating Cards */}
        <div class="hidden md:flex w-full md:w-1/2 relative justify-center">
          <div
            class="relative w-full max-w-lg aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 shadow-2xl group"
          >
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
              alt="Dashboard overview"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
              loading="lazy"
            />

            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/10 dark:bg-secondary/40 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500"
            >
            </div>

            {/* Floating Card 1: +124% Conversão */}
            <div
              class="absolute top-8 left-8 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 animate-bounce"
              style="animation-duration: 3.5s;"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-500/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-600 dark:text-green-400"
                    >trending_up</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p
                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-medium"
                  >
                    +124%
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-text-main dark:text-white">
                    Conversão
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Floating Card 2: Lançamento Sucesso */}
            <div
              class="absolute bottom-12 right-6 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 animate-bounce"
              style="animation-duration: 4.2s; animation-delay: 1.5s;"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-accent/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent"
                    >rocket_launch</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p
                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-medium"
                  >
                    Lançamento
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-text-main dark:text-white">
                    Sucesso
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== SOCIAL PROOF / STATS SECTION ===== */}
  <section
    class="bg-gradient-to-r from-surface-dark to-[#0f1424] border-y border-white/5 text-white py-12 md:py-16 px-5 md:px-12 w-full relative"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-10 blur-[1px]"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 relative z-10"
    >
      {/* Stats */}
      <div
        class="flex justify-between items-end md:items-center border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-white/10 pb-6 md:pb-0 md:pr-16 w-full md:w-auto"
      >
        <div class="md:mr-16">
          <p class="text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-1 md:mb-2">
            100+
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300 font-medium">
            PMEs Atendidas
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right md:text-left">
          <p class="text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-1 md:mb-2">
            98%
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300 font-medium">
            Retenção de Clientes
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Certification Badge */}
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/5 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm flex-1 max-w-md"
      >
        <div class="bg-accent/20 p-3 rounded-full shrink-0">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-3xl"
            >verified_user</span
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg mb-1">
            Parceiro Regional Certificado
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            Reconhecimento pela excelência em tecnologia e inovação.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== SERVICES GRID ===== */}
  <section class="px-5 md:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 w-full bg-[#050505]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      {/* Header */}
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10 md:mb-16 md:text-center md:items-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          O que entregamos
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl">
          Soluções completas e integradas para escalar seu negócio de ponta a
          ponta com máxima eficiência.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Services Grid - 4 Cards with Different Colors */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8">
        {/* Service 1: Development - Blue */}
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col p-6 md:p-8 bg-background-light dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2rem] border border-transparent hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-5 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px] md:text-[32px]"
              >devices</span
            >
          </div>
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white text-lg md:text-xl mb-2"
          >
            Desenvolvimento Web
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Seu melhor vendedor trabalhando 24h. Sites velozes, com SEO afiado e
            programados para captar clientes.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Service 2: Copywriting - Purple */}
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col p-6 md:p-8 bg-background-light dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2rem] border border-transparent hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-5 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px] md:text-[32px]"
              >edit_note</span
            >
          </div>
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white text-lg md:text-xl mb-2"
          >
            Copywriting
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Textos estratégicos e persuasivos que vendem o seu produto 24/7.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Service 3: Automation - Orange */}
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col p-6 md:p-8 bg-background-light dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2rem] border border-transparent hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 mb-5 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px] md:text-[32px]"
              >smart_toy</span
            >
          </div>
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white text-lg md:text-xl mb-2"
          >
            Automação Sob Medida
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            De agendamentos via WhatsApp com IA a fluxos de atendimento
            exclusivos, criamos sistemas que trabalham por você.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Service 4: Diagnosis - Green */}
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col p-6 md:p-8 bg-background-light dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2rem] border border-transparent hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-5 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px] md:text-[32px]"
              >analytics</span
            >
          </div>
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white text-lg md:text-xl mb-2"
          >
            Diagnóstico
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Análise profunda de dados do seu mercado para decisões precisas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== PROCESS SECTION (4 STEPS) ===== */}
  <section
    class="py-16 md:py-24 px-5 md:px-12 relative overflow-hidden w-full bg-secondary"
  >
    {/* Dot Pattern Background */}
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.05]"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(currentColor 1.5px, transparent 1.5px); background-size: 30px 30px;"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      {/* Header */}
      <div class="md:text-center md:mb-16 mb-10">
        <h2
          class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4"
        >
          Como trabalhamos
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Uma metodologia provada, dividida em quatro passos claros para levar o
          seu negócio rumo ao sucesso contínuo.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Timeline */}
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between gap-0 md:gap-8 border-l-2 md:border-l-0 md:border-t-2 border-white/10 ml-3 md:ml-0 md:pt-8 w-full"
      >
        {/* Step 1: Diagnóstico */}
        <div class="pl-8 md:pl-0 pb-10 md:pb-0 relative md:flex-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -left-[9px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 md:-top-[43px] top-0 w-4 md:w-6 h-4 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 md:border-8 border-secondary shadow-sm"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="md:text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 md:mb-3">
              1. Diagnóstico
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base">
              Entendemos profundamente o seu negócio, concorrentes e
              identificamos gargalos focais.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 2: Estratégia */}
        <div class="pl-8 md:pl-0 pb-10 md:pb-0 relative md:flex-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -left-[9px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 md:-top-[43px] top-0 w-4 md:w-6 h-4 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-4 md:border-8 border-secondary shadow-sm"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="md:text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 md:mb-3">
              2. Estratégia
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base">
              Criamos um plano de ação tático e personalizado focado em ROI
              (retorno sobre investimento).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 3: Execução */}
        <div class="pl-8 md:pl-0 pb-10 md:pb-0 relative md:flex-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -left-[9px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 md:-top-[43px] top-0 w-4 md:w-6 h-4 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-4 md:border-8 border-secondary shadow-sm"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="md:text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 md:mb-3">
              3. Execução
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base">
              Implementamos as soluções aprovadas utilizando as melhores e mais
              recentes tecnologias do mercado.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 4: Otimização */}
        <div class="pl-8 md:pl-0 pb-2 md:pb-0 relative md:flex-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -left-[9px] md:left-1/2 md:-ml-3 md:-top-[43px] top-0 w-4 md:w-6 h-4 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-accent border-4 md:border-8 border-secondary shadow-sm"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="md:text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 md:mb-3">
              4. Otimização
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base">
              Monitoramento, testes e acompanhamento contínuo para ganho e
              melhoria de resultados a longo prazo.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ===== FAQ SECTION ===== */}
  <section class="px-5 md:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 w-full">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      {/* Header */}
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8 md:mb-12 md:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          Dúvidas Comuns
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base md:text-lg">
          As principais perguntas que recebemos dos nossos novos clientes.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* FAQ Items */}
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <details
          class="group bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white p-5 md:p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-base md:text-lg hover:bg-gray-100/50 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Qual o prazo de entrega padrão?</span>
            <span
              class="transition group-open:rotate-180 material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-1 rounded-full shadow-sm"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-base px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Depende estritamente do escopo do projeto e funcionalidades pedidas.
            No entanto, para sites institucionais completos, costumam ser
            entregues entre 15 a 30 dias úteis após a aprovação do briefing
            inicial.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details
          class="group bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white p-5 md:p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-base md:text-lg hover:bg-gray-100/50 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Vocês atendem clientes fora da região de origem?</span>
            <span
              class="transition group-open:rotate-180 material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-1 rounded-full shadow-sm"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-base px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Totalmente! Somos uma agência digital nativa, por isso atendemos
            empresas e clientes em todo o Brasil (e no exterior) de forma 100%
            remota com a mesma proximidade, suporte e eficiência de um trabalho
            local.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details
          class="group bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white p-5 md:p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-base md:text-lg hover:bg-gray-100/50 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Quanto custa o serviço na média?</span>
            <span
